<p class="">Is it the view of the Prime Minister that the decision come to by the Government has definitely settled this controversy, and will he use his influence to prevent it being continued as an internecine warfare between the two Departments? If it has not been settled it is no use pretending that it has, and we shall have this constant firing between the Departments over and over again.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
