<p class="">The Government decision, as taken, and now made public, is final. As far as it can settle the controversy it has settled it. We cannot prevent individuals from still firing shots but we hope they will refrain from doing so, because it is desirable in the public interest that this controversy should be settled.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
