<p class="">I beg to give notice that I will raise this matter to-day. I would also further ask the Prime Minister to consider whether the Minister for the Co-ordination of Defence can make a short statement so that we shall not be beating the air.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
